channel.title: Moparscape not starting... Never happend before
channel.description:
:eek:
I'm not new to moparscape, or a noob, but I am getting an error I never got before...
When I start up moparscape, I get "Sorry, an error has occured whilst loading Runescape" In big yellow letters, followed by 5 solutions.
Anyone? :confused:
edit: at the bottom, it says error: loaderror bobstarting up 20.
